{"tid":2276614,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"如果證實有選舉舞弊 但合法票數都仲係登贏","createTime":"2020-11-08T02:44:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-08T03:43:12.000Z","uid":24332,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a5143f1901885e78c0178f10f144a0a11bf9471a","tid":2276614,"uid":24332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T02:44:57.000Z","msg":"如題<br />\n如果證實到到有選舉舞弊<br />\n例如 種票 死人票 假票 中共印票 等等<br />\n但合法票數計都仲係拜登贏<br />\n咁會點？<br />\n<br />\n正路諗應該由法院宣布取消拜登資格？<br />\n<br />\n但諗諗吓拜登團隊只要搵個替死鬼認咗佢<br />\n拜登堅稱自己事前唔知道情況<br />\n佢又可以走甩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a72f7152cf13b46e8197b3a03e4aefdc6656a189","tid":2276614,"uid":3457,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T02:48:05.000Z","msg":"有舞弊 選舉結果應該係直頭唔計"},{"pid":"e542a331f2675cf10f08c71e5e8b4437eee380e5","tid":2276614,"uid":74361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T02:49:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://j.gifs.com/0YQ767.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fj.gifs.com%2F0YQ767.gif&h=d30181cb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a3e132fb96808e489c7b6f10054c8c8acd9693bd","tid":2276614,"uid":103929,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T02:50:02.000Z","msg":"d票唔見嗮<br />\n你點重新計算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n肯定只能重選"},{"pid":"8087922cca1905290502b9fa7cc7ba10d255bf9e","tid":2276614,"uid":126782,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T02:52:58.000Z","msg":"如果影響唔到結果 法庭唔會介入大選結果<br />\n<br />\n要尊重選民意志"},{"pid":"700882c1d6807ac2bfc5d3662a84f7280e65e7a9","tid":2276614,"uid":189638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-08T03:43:12.000Z","msg":"睇下法庭點判啦，最簡單就係重選，搵聯邦嘅人去監票<br />\n<br />\n而票數接近，而又有證據嘅話，DQ某組嘅票，如果本身就係接近被DQ嘅就會逆轉"}]}